1014
01:15:30.708 --> 01:15:32.833
You can tell me your bitter truth.

1015
01:15:39.750 --> 01:15:41.708
My full name is Hamza Ali Mazari.

1016
01:15:43.250 --> 01:15:45.083
I work for Rehman Baloch's gang.

1017
