1049
01:18:54.583 --> 01:18:56.208
this evidence will be useful.

1050
01:18:57.833 --> 01:18:58.708
Yes. sir.

1051
01:19:00.166 --> 01:19:01.083
And Bansal.

1052
01:19:02.708 --> 01:19:04.875
