Major Iqbal is on his way here
following a meeting with Zarwari <i>sahab.</i>

1061
01:20:28.500 --> 01:20:30.333
Welcome.
Rehman <i>bhai.</i>

1062
01:20:31.875 --> 01:20:33.250
Meet Sajid Mir from Lashkar.

1063
01:20:34.625 --> 01:20:36.083
Abdul Bhuttovi
and Azam Cheema.

1064
01:20:36.458 --> 01:20:37.375
Sir.

1065
